<div class="title">Experimental Dosing</div>
<div class="substance">2C-B</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Molish&Exact=1">Molish</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Molish. "Experimental Dosing: An Experience with 2C-B (exp32811)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Apr 6, 2006. erowid.org/exp/32811</div>

<br/>



